{"tid":2398442,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Facebook 先至係最保障個人資料嘅平臺","createTime":"2021-02-07T09:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T04:02:49.000Z","uid":244168,"like":636,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe3d5e6df336a5ad49e991355842b7d8ce99766","tid":2398442,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"話說我張信用卡無端端有來自fb嘅交易記錄，大概3000蚊左右<br />\n<br />\n我就當然即刻走去問啦，希望佢哋可以話到俾我知邊個用咗我張信用卡，最好就退返錢畀我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAP0YrW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAP0YrW.png&h=90e0b8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZsU2TF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZsU2TF.png&h=cf0a368f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bho87km.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBho87km.png&h=0b9cecdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nfb明知張卡係我嘅，亦都明知係另外一個人用緊，但係佢哋都選擇唔話俾我知邊個人用緊，選擇保障賊仔嘅行為。我亦都相當肯定，自己張卡冇俾任何人使用過。<br />\n<br />\n所以話，如果做一啲不法嘅行徑，有啲人會要你用BTC，我覺得哩啲已經outdate，最好更係要用facebook la"},{"pid":"bce18d407c15e4e5d25ab4f444be2fffa99b996a","tid":2398442,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f81da09292eb80d8b55927e119b5460025f671ab","tid":2398442,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:55:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34cc41509930c426eb948b78e4cc2487e2ba80fd","tid":2398442,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:55:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e1d7c9a27917a6e93f43b087aeaf6e26e05cd0c","tid":2398442,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:55:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd45c815c7c77b3248f389f8522d928ca6b66ca7","tid":2398442,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1647cc432536260a82dd738e93aa42bc7e1e